layout.p:
Columns: 226;
                                                  ruled lines: 51;
                                                  written lines: 51; Uniform layout. Ruling by hard point.Visible pricking and stiching. Made up of a number of fragments pieced together. 226 columns in total, one to seven columns per membrane. No tagin, except for three tagin on שעטנזגץ in Ex. 14:28-20:21. The letter ח is arched in some of the fragments. Majuscular and minuscular letter in accordance with the rules. Special shape of the letter פ occurs frequently, inverted נ is placed before and after Num. 10:35-36.  The "puncta extraordinaria" placed on the words fixed by masorah.
